00:18:46.150 --> 00:18:49.600
Sondy: particular on the featherweights but modern machines are

00:18:49.600 --> 00:18:52.660
Sondy: very similar into how that all works. So it's just a really

00:18:52.750 --> 00:18:56.380
Sondy: cool way to sort of fundamentally understand how

00:18:57.940 --> 00:19:01.530
Sondy: sewing machines have evolved and haven't evolved and how to use

00:19:01.650 --> 00:19:05.820
Sondy: them. And I feel like it informs better how I use my

00:19:06.540 --> 00:19:12.210
